# Linear Time Approach
```
class Solution {
public:
    int sum(int num1, int num2) {
    return (num1) + log(abs(abs(num1)/2+num2/4 + num1*6 - 112/log(num2) + log(num2)-412)/2*log(2)*4 + log(1) + log(1)/2)/log(abs(abs(num1)/2+num2/4 + num1*6 - 112/log(num2) + log(num2)-412)/2*log(2)*4 + log(1) + log(1)/2) + (num2 - 1);
    }
};
```
